  "answer": "Permit types showed mixed growth rates compared to last year. Development Services (DS) permits decreased by 9.4% (from 1,181 to 1,070), Electrical Permits (EP) dropped by 3.2% (from 16,683 to 16,149), and Plumbing Permits (PP) fell by 3.0% (from 15,035 to 14,590). However, Building Permits (BP) increased by 2.6% (from 11,545 to 11,846), and Mechanical Permits (MP) rose slightly by 0.5% (from 10,373 to 10,430).",
